{"sta":1,"data":{"subTitle":"悬挂式布局","content":"<p>有时，主栏的左侧或右侧，需要添加一个图片栏。<a href=\"/app/data/css3/flex/case/media.html\" target=\"_blank\">查看Demo</a></p><p><img src=\"/app/data/css3/flex/img/bg2015071325.png\" alt=\"\" title=\"\"></p><p>HTML代码如下。</p><pre><code>\n<span><span><span>&lt;</span>div</span> <span>class</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span>Media<span>\"</span></span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n  <span><span><span>&lt;</span>img</span> <span>class</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span>Media-figure<span>\"</span></span> <span>src</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span><span>\"</span></span> <span>alt</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span><span>\"</span></span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n  <span><span><span>&lt;</span>p</span> <span>class</span><span><span>=</span><span>\"</span>Media-body<span>\"</span></span><span>&gt;</span></span>...<span><span><span>&lt;/</span>p</span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n<span><span><span>&lt;/</span>div</span><span>&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre><p>CSS代码如下。</p><pre><code>\n<span>.Media </span><span>{</span>\n  <span>display</span><span>:</span> flex<span>;</span>\n  <span>align-items</span><span>:</span> flex-start<span>;</span>\n<span>}</span>\n\n<span>.Media-figure </span><span>{</span>\n  <span>margin-right</span><span>:</span> 1em<span>;</span>\n<span>}</span>\n\n<span>.Media-body </span><span>{</span>\n  <span>flex</span><span>:</span> 1<span>;</span>\n<span>}</span></code></pre>"}}